hadiths[68]{hadithnumber,text}:
1720,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' resham ka libas aur sona meri ummat key mardon par haram hai aur un ki aurton key liye halal kya gaya hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , Aqba bin Aamir , Anas , Huzefa , Umme-Haani , Abdullah bin Amr , Imran bin Husain , Abdullah bin Zuber , Jabir , abu Rehan, ibne-Umar , Bara , aur Waasila Isqaa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1721,"umr ney maqam Jaabiya mein khutba diya aur kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney resham sey mana farmaya siwaye do, ya teen, ya chaar angusht key barabar. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1722,"Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur Zuber bin Awam Raziallahu anhuma ney eik ghazwa mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey juon ki shikayat ki, to aap ney unhen resham ki qamis ki ijazat dey di, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey unkey badan par resham ki qamis dekhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1723,"Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) hamarey paas ( aaye to main unkey paas gaya, unhoney puchha : tum kon ho? mainey kaha : main Waqid bin Amr bin Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) hun, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ro padey aur boley : tum Saad ki shakal key ho, Saad badey daraz qad aur lambey they, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik reshmi jubba bheja gaya jis mein zari ka kaam kya huwa tha padhi. aap usey pehan kar member par chadhey , khadey huye ya bethey to log usey chu kar kehney lagey : hamney aaj ki tarah kabhi koi kapda nahin dekha , aap ney farmaya : '' kya tum is par tajjub kar rahey ho? jannat mein Saad key rumaal is sey kahin behtar hain jo tum dekh rahey ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Asma bint abi Bakr sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1724,"mainey surkh jodey mein kisi lambey baal waley ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey khoobsurat nahin dekha , aap key baal shaanon ko chhootey they, aap key shaanon key darmiyan doori thi, aap na kotaah qad they aur na lambey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Samra, abu-Ramsa aur abu-Juhaifa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1725,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey qassi key baney huye reshmi aur zard rang key kapdey pehanney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1726,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ghi, paneer aur posteen ( chamdey ka libas ( key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' halal wo hai jisey Allah ney apni kitab mein halal kar diya, aur haram wo hai, jisey Allah ney apni kitab mein haram kar diya aur jis chiz key barey mein wo khamosh raha wo us qabeel sey hai jisey Allah ney maaf kar diya hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain, 2- isey Sufiyan ney basanad (سليمان التيمي an أبي عثمان an سلمان) moqufan riwayat kya hai, goya ye maqoof hadees ziyada sahih hai, is baab mein Mughira sey bhi hadees aai hai, 2- mainey Imam Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha : to unhoney kaha : main is ko mehfooz nahin samajhta hun, Sufiyan ney basanad (سليمان التيمي an أبي عثمان an سلمان) moqufan riwayat ki hai, 4- Imam Bukhari kehtey hain : saif bin Harun maqaribul-hadees hain, aur Saif-bin-Muhammad Aasim sey riwayat karney mein ذاہب الحدیث hain."
1727,"eik bakri mar gaee, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bakri waley sey kaha : tum ney uski khaal kyon na utaar li? phir tum dabaaghat dey kar us sey faeyda hasil kartey padhi. ."
1728,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis chamdey ko dabaaghat di gaee , wo pak ho gaya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- b-wasta ibne-Abbas Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri sanadon sey bhi isi tarah marvi hai, 3- ye hadees ibne-Abbas sey kabhi Memuna key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aur kabhi sauda key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai, 4- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi ibne-Abbas ki hadees aur Memuna key wastey sey marvi ibne-Abbas ki hadees ko sahih kehtey huye suna, unhoney kaha : ehtimaal hai ke ibne-Abbas ney b-wasta Memuna Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya ho, aur ibne-Abbas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey barahe-raast bhi riwayat kya, aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Sufiyan Sory, ibne-Mubarak, Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, 5- Nazar bin Shumeil ney bhi iska yehi mafhoom bayan kya hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : Nazar bin Shumeil ney kaha : « إهاب » us janwer key chamdey ko kaha jata hai, jiska gosht khaya jata hai, 6- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain : murdar ka chamdaa dabaaghat deney key baad pak ho jata hai'', 7- Shafai kehtey hain : kuttey aur Sura key ilawa jis murdar janwer ka chamda dabaaghat diya jaey wo pak ho jaeyga, unhoney isi hadees sey istidlaal kya hai, 8- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ney darindon key chamdon ko makrooh samjha hai, agar-che us ko dabaaghat di gaee ho, Abdullah bin Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, un logon ney isey pehanney aur is mein namaz ada karney ko bura samjha hai, 9- Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qol « أيما إهاب دبغ فقد طهر » ka matlab ye hai ke us janwer ka chamda dabaghat sey pak ho jaeyga jis ka gosht khaya jata hai, 10- is bab mein Salma bin Mohbiq, Memuna aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1729,"hamarey paas Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka khat aaya ke tum log murda janweron key chamdey padhi. aur putthon sey faaedey na hasil karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- ye hadees Abdullah bin Akeem sey unkey shuyokh key wastey sey bhi aai hai, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka is par amal nahin hai, 4- Abdullah bin Akeem sey ye hadees marvi hai, unhoney kaha : hamarey paas Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka khat aap ki wafat sey do maah pehley aaya, 5- mainey Ahmed bin Hasan ko kehtey suna, Ahmed bin Hanbal isi hadees ko ikhtiyar kartey they is wajeh sey ke is mein aap ki wafat sey do maah qabl ka zikr hai, wo ye bhi kehtey they : ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka aakhiri hukm tha, 6- phir Ahmed bin Hanbal ney is hadees ko chhod diya isliye ke raawiyon sey iski sanad mein iztirab waqey hai, chunanche baaz log usey Abdullah bin Akeem sey unkey juhaina key shuyukh key wastey sey riwayat kartey hain."
1730,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala qiyamat key din us shakhs ki taraf nahin dekhega jisney takabbur sey apna teh band ghaseeta''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzaifa, abu Saeed Khudri, abu-Huraira, Samra, abu-Zar, Aaisha aur wuhaib bin Mughaffal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1731,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs takabbur sey apna kapda ghasiteyga Allah Taala qiyamat key din uski taraf nahin dekheyga.''  Umme-Salma ney kaha : aurten apney daamanon ka kya karen? aap ney farmaya : ''eik baalisht latka lein'' , unhoney kaha : tab to unkey qadam khul jaeyngey, aap ney farmaya : ''eik baalisht latkaaey aur is sey ziyada na latkaaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1732,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fatima key « نطاق » key liye eik baalisht ka andaza lagaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- baaz logon ney isey :(حماد بن سلمة an علي بن زيد an الحسن an أمه an أم سلمة) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. 2- is hadees mein aurton key liye teh-band (chadar) ghaseetney ki ijazat hai, isliye ke ye unkey liye ziyada sattar poshi ka baais hai."
1733,Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney hamarey samney eik ooni chadar aur mota teh-band nikala aur kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat inhi dono kapdon mein hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali aur ibne-Masood Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain.
1734,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis din Musa (Alaihissalam) sey unkey rab ney guftgu ki us din Musa (Alaihissalam) key badan par purani chadar , ooni jubba , ooni topii , aur ooni saraawil (paajama) tha aur unkey jootey marey huye gadhey key chamdey key they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai hum isey sirf Humed Aaraj ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Humed sey murad Humed bin Ali Koofi hain. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna ke Humed bin Ali Aaraj hadees ke munkir hain aur Humed bin Qais Aaraj Makki jo Mujahid key shagrid hain, wo bharosemand hain. 3- « کمہ » : chhoti topi ko kehtey hain."
1735,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Fateh Makka key din Makka mein is haal mein dakhil huye ke aap key sar par siyah amama tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Ali , umr , ibne Hurriyas , ibne-Abbas aur Rukna (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1736,"jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam amama baandhtey to usey apney shaanon key bech latka letey. Nafey kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma apney amama ko shaanon key bech latkaate they. Ubedullah bin umr kehtey hain : mainey Qasim aur Salim ko bhi aisa kartey huye dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, lekin un ki hadees sanad key aetbar sey sahih nahin hai."
1737,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey soney ki angoothi, «Qassi» (eik reshmi kapde) ka libas , rukoo aur sujood mein Quran padhney aur «muasfar» ( kusum sey rangey huye zard ( kapdey sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1738,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney soney ki angoothi sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Imran ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1739,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki angoothi chaandi ki thi aur uska nageena (aqeeq) Habsha ka bana huwa tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Barida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
1740,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki angoothi chaandi ki thi, uska nageena bhi usi ka tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1741,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney soney ki eik angoothi banai aur isey dahiney haath mein pehna , phir member par bethey aur farmaya : ''main ney us angoothi ko apney dahiney haath mein pehna tha'' , phir aap ney isey nikal kar phenka aur logon ney bhi apni anguthiyan phenk den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ba-wasta Nafey ibne-Umar sey dusri sanad sey isi tarah aai hai, is mein unhoney ye zikr kiya ke aap ney dahiney haath mein angoothi pahni. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , Abdullah bin Jaafar , ibne-Abbas , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1742,mainey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko dahiney haath mein angoothi pehney dekha aur mera yehi khayal hai ke unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dahiney haath mein angoothi pehney dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney kaha : Salat bin Abdullah bin Naufal key wastey sey Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat Hasan sahih hai.
1743,Hasan aur Husain apney baaeyn hath mein angoothi pehantey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1744,"mainey ibne-Abi Raafey padhi. ko dahiney haath mein angoothi pehantey dekha to iskey barey mein un sey puchha to unhoney kaha ke mainey Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dahiney haath mein angoothi pehantey dekha , Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney dahiney haath mein angoothi pehantey they. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ye is baab mein sab sey sahih riwayat hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1745,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chaandi ki eik angoothi banai, is mein (Muhammad Rasoolullah) naqsh karaya , phir farmaya : ''tum log apni angoothi par ye naqsh mat karana.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. (لا تنقشوا عليه) ka matlab ye hai ke aap ney mana farmaya koi doosra apni angoothi par (Muhammad Rasoolullah) naqsh kiraaey ۔"
1746,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab pakhana jatey to apni angoothi utaar detey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1747,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki angoothi ka naqsh is tarah tha. (Muhammad) eik laain mein, (Rasool) eik laain mein aur (Allah) eik laain mein.  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1748,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki anguthi ka naqsh teen laainon mein tha « Muhammad » eik laain mein, « Rasool » eik laain mein aur « Allah » eik laain mein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muhammad bin Yahya ney apni riwayat mein teen laainon ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai."
1749,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghar mein tasweer rakhney sey mana farmaya aur aap ney isko bananey sey bhi mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , abu-Talha , Aaisha Abu-Hurera aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1750,"wo Abu-Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat karney unkey ghar gaey, to mainey unkey paas Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) ko paya , abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aadmi ko wo chadar nikalney key liye bulaya jo unkey nichey thi, Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : kyon nikal rahey hain? unhoney kaha : isliye ke is mein taswiren hain, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is silsiley mein jo kuch farmaya hai usey aap jantey hain, Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aap ney to ye bhi farmaya hai : siwaye us kapdey key jis mein naqsh ho abu-Talha ney kaha : aap ney to ye farmaya hai lekin ye merey liye ziyada achchha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1751,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney koi tasweer banai Allah Taala us ko azab deta rahega yahan tak ke musawwir (chitrkaar) is mein rooh phunk dey aur wo is mein rooh nahin phunk sakeyga, aur jisney kisi qom ki baat kaan laga kar suni halanke wo us sey bhagtey hon padhi. , qiyamat key din uskey kaan mein seesa dala jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood , Abu-Hurera , abu-Hujefa , Aaisha aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1752,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baal ki safedi (khizaab key zarie) badal dalo aur Yahud ki mushaabihat na ikhtiyar karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey marfoo tareeqe sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 3- is bab mein Zuber , ibne-Abbas , Jabir , Abu-Zar , Anas , Jahdama , abu-Tufail , Jabir bin Samura , abu-Hujefa aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1753,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtar chiz jis sey baal ki safedi badli jaey wo mehndi aur vasma hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1754,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam darmiyaanaa qad they, aap na lambey they na chhota qad, gandumi rang key sudol jism waley they, aap key baal na ghungraale they na sidhey, aap jab chaltey to pair utha kar chaltey jaise koi ooper sey nichey utarta hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey Humed ki riwayat sey Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Bara , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Abbas , abu-Saeed , Jabir , Wayl bin Hajar aur Umme-Haani (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1755,"mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik hi bartan sey ghusl karti thi, aap key baal « جمہ » sey chhotey aur « وفرہ » sey badey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- dusri sanadon sey ye hadees Aaisha sey yun marvi (riwayat hui) hai, kehti hain : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik hi bartan sey ghusl karti thi, raawiyon ney is hadees mein ye jumla nahin bayan kiya hai, ( وكان له شعر فوق الجمة ودون الوفرة). 3- Abdur-Rehman bin abi Zanaad Bharosemand hain, Malik bin Anas un ki tauseeq kartey they aur un ki riwayat likhney ka hukm detey they."
1756,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kanghi karney sey mana farmaya , siwaye iskey ke naagha kar key ki jaey."
1757,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ismid surma lagaao isliye ke wo beenai ko chamkaata hai aur palkon ka baal ugata hai'' , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik surme-daani thi jis sey aap har raat teen silaai is (daahini aankh) mein aur teen silaai is (baain aankh) mein surma lagatey they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum is lafz key sath sirf Ibaad bin Mansoor ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1758,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do libas sey mana farmaya : ''eik samma, aur doosra ye ke koi shakhs khud ko kapdey mein is tarah lapet ley ke uski sharmgaah par us kapdey ka koi hissea na rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye dusri sanadon sey bhi Abu-Hurera key wastey sey marfoo tareeqe sey aai hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Umar , Aaisha , abu-Saeed , Jabir aur abu-Umama sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1759,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney baal mein jodey laganey wali , baal mein jodey lagwaaney wali , gudna gondne wali aur gudna gudwane wali par lanat bheji hai.'' Nafey kehtey hain :gudna masude mein hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , ibne-Masood , Asma binte abi Bakr , ibne-Abbas , Maaqil bin Yasar aur Muawiya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1760,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum ko reshmi zeen par sawar honey sey mana farmaya : Raavi kehtey hain : is hadees main eik qissa mazkur (zikr hua) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali aur Muawiya Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, Shoba ney bhi Ash-as bin abi Sha'sa sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, is hadees main eik qissa mazkur hai."
1761,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jis bichhoney par sotey they wo chamdey ka tha, uskey andar khajoor key darkht ki chhaal bhari hui thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Hafsa aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1762,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nazdik sab sey pasandida libas qamis thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abdul Momin bin Khalid ki riwayat sey jantey hain, wo isey riwayat karney mein munfarid (alag) hain, wo Marvazi hain. 3- baaz logon ney is hadees ko is sanad sey riwayat ki hai : (عن أبي تميلة an عبد المؤمن بن خالد an عبد الله بن بريدة an أمه an أم سلمة)."
1763,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nazdik sab sey pasandida libas qamis thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Ismail ko kehtey suna : Abdullah bin Barida ki hadees jo unki maa key wastey sey Umme-Salma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ziyada sahih hai, abu-Tameela is hadees mein (عن امہ) ka wasta zarur bayan kartey they."
1764,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key nazdik pasandida libas qamis thi.
1765,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key bazu ki aasteen kalaai (pahunchun) tak hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
1766,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam qamis pehantey to daahini taraf sey (pehanna) shuru kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : kaee logon ney ye hadees basanad « Shoba an abi Hurera » maqoof riwayat ki hai, Shoba sey riwayat karney waley Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-waaris key ilawa hum nahin jantey ke kisi ney isey marfoo tareeqe sey riwayat kiya hai."
1767,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam koi naya kapda pehantey to uska naam letey jaisey amama (pagdi), qamis ya chadar , phir kehtey : (اللهم لك الحمد أنت كسوتنيه أسألك خيره وخير ما صنع له وأعوذ بك من شره وشر ما صنع له) ''Allah ! terey hi liye tareef hai, tu ney hi mujhey ye pehnaya hai, main tum sey iski khair aur us chiz ki khair ka talabgaar hun jis key liye ye banaya gaya hai, aur iski shar aur is chiz key shar sey teri panah maangta hun jis key liye ye banaya gaya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1768,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Romi jubba pehna jiski aasteenein tang thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1769,"Dahiya Kalbi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye do mozey tohfa bhejey, chunanche aap ney unhen pehnaa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Israel ney apni riwayat mein kaha hai) jisey wo ba-tareeq « an Jabir » riwayat kartey hain : eik jubba bhi bheja , aap ney un dono mozon ko pehnaa yahan tak ke wo phat gaey, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nahin jantey they ke wo zabah kiye jaane wale janwer ki khaal key hain ya ghair zabah kiye jaane wale. 3- Abu-Is'haq Sabeei ka naam Suleman (Alaihissalam) hai. 4- Hasan bin Ayash abu-Bakar bin Ayash key bhai hain."
1770,"jahiliyat key dinon mein kilaab padhi. (eik ladaai ( key din meri naak kat gaee , mainey chaandi ki eik naak lagai to us sey badbu aaney lagi , isliye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey soney ki eik naak laganey ka hukm diya padhi. . is sanad sey bhi abu-Shahab sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat hai, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin tarfa ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Salim bin Zareer ney bhi Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa sey abu-Shahab ki hadees jaisi riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kaee eik sey riwayat hai ke unhoney apney daanton ko soney ( key taar ( sey baandha, is hadees mein unkey liye daleel mojud hai, 4- Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney (Salam bin Zareer key bajaey) Salam bin Zarrin kaha hai, yahan un sey weham huwa hai Wazrir ziyada sahih hai, Raavi abu-Saeed Saghani ka naam Muhammad bin Muyassar hai."
1771,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney darindon ki khaal ( istimal karney ( sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye ziyada sahih hai.
1772,"mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jootey kaisey they? kaha : unkey do tasmey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1773,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key jootay key do tasmey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas o Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1774,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi aadmi eik joota pehan kar na chaley, dono pehan ley ya dono utaar dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1775,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya ke koi shakhs khadey ho kar joota pehney padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Ubedullah bin umr Warqi ney is hadees ko Maamar sey , Maamar ney Qatada sey , Qatada ney Anas sey riwayat ki hai, ye dono hadisein muhaddeseen key nazdik sahih nahin hain, Haris bin nabhaan ka hafiza muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hai, 3- Qatada ki Anas sey marvi hadees ki hum koi asal nahin jantey hain."
1776,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khadey ho kar joota pehanney sey mana farmaya. ٍ Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih nahin hai, aur na hi Maamar ki hadees jisey wo Ammar bin abi Ammar sey aur Ammar Abu-Hurera sey riwayat kartey hain."
1777,kabhi-kabhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik joota pehan kar chaltey.
1778,"wo eik joota pehan kar chalen . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai, 2- Sufiyan Sory aur kaee logon ney isi tarah is hadees ko Abdur-Rehman bin Qasim key wastey sey moqoof tareeq sey riwayat kya hai aur ye moqoof riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
1779,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey jab koi joota pehney to dahiney pair sey shuru karey aur jab utarey to baaein sey shuru kerey. pehanney mein dahina paaon pehley aur utaarney mein peechey ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1780,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''agar tum (aakhirat mein) mujh sey milna chahti ho to duniya sey musafir key saman safar key barabar hasil karney par iktifa karo, maaldaaron ki sohbat sey bacho aur kisi kapdey ko us waqt tak puraana na samajh yahan tak ke is mein pewand laga lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Saleh bin Hassan ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Saleh bin Hassan munkire-hadees hain aur Saleh bin abi Hassan jin sey ibne-Abi Zi-ib ney riwayat ki hai wo Suqa hain"
1781,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka is haal mein aaye ke aap ki chaar chotiyan thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Umme-Haani sey Mujahid ka samaa, main nahin janta hun."
1782,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba ki aasteenein kushada thin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees munkar hai, 2- Abdullah bin Basar Basra key rehney waley hain, muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, Yahya bin Saeed waghera ney unhen zaeef kaha hai, 3- « بطح » chodi aur kushada chiz ko kehtey hain."
1783,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni ya meri pindli ka gosht pakda aur farmaya : '' ye tehband ki jagah hai, agar is par razi na ho to thoda aur neecha kar lo , phir agar aur neecha karna chaho to tehband takhnon sey neecha nahin kar saktey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Sory aur Shoba ney bhi us ko Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey riwayat kya hai."
1784,"Rukana ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kushti ladi to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney usey pachhaad diya, Rukana kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna : '' hamarey aur mushrikon key darmiyan farq topiyon par amaama baandhney ka hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- iski sanad qaaim ( sahih ( nahin hai, 3- hum abul-Hasan Asqalani aur ibn Rukana ko nahin jantey hain."
1785,"eik aadmi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas lohey ki angoothi pehan kar aaya, aap ney farmaya : '' kya baat hai main dekh raha hun ke tum jahannamiyon ka zewar pehney ho? '' phir wo aap key paas peetal ki anguthi pehan kar aaya, aap ney farmaya : ''kya baat hai ke tum sey buton ki badbu aa rahi hai? phir wo aap key paas soney ki anguthi pehan kar aaya, to aap ney farmaya : '' kya baat hai main dekh raha hun ke tum jannatiyon ka zewar pehney ho? usney puchha : main kis chiz ki anguthi pehnun? aap ney farmaya : '' chaandi ki aur (wazan mein) eik Misqal sey kam rakho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Abdullah bin Muslim ki kunniyat abu-Taiba hai aur wo Abdullah bin Muslim Maruzi hain."
1786,mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney «qassi» (eik reshmi kapda ( surkh ( rang ka reshmi ( zeen posh aur us ungli aur us ungli mein angoothi pehanney sey mana farmaya aur unhoney shahadat aur beech ki ungli ki taraf ishara kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1787,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka pasandida kapda jisey aap pehantey they wo dhaari daar yamni chadar thi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
